  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "MystACL™ Z IP is an outdoor ready (IP65) high-performance LED bar loaded with 10* 40W OSRAM™ Ostar 4-in-1 RGBW LEDs. It offers DMX control with full pixel mapping capabilities, plus 3° to 60° zoom, creating effects that can range from a narrow angled light curtain to a wide angled wash.\n\n\nMystACL™ Z IP features 210° motorized tilt (8-16 bit) plus unique 3-layer pixel set & macro effects, multiple built-in programs, color presets, 3/5-pin DMX + RJ45 input/output connections (Art-Net ready), and powerCON® TRUE1-compatible power input/output connections.",
